  "description": "A vibrant nighttime scene showcasing a fireworks display over a city skyline and a long bridge. The fireworks burst in shades of red, white, and gold, creating a spectacular display against the dark sky. Below, the city is illuminated with numerous lights, forming a dense urban landscape. A prominent bridge, adorned with lights, spans across a body of water, connecting the foreground to the city. The water reflects some of the city lights and the glow of the fireworks, adding to the overall luminosity. The composition provides a sweeping view, emphasizing the scale of both the natural and built environments.",
